{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"38514-nila-pari","title":"নীল পরি","description":"নীল পরি দুটি ছোট্ট মেয়ের গল্প। কল্পনার এক নীল পরির সাথে তাদের দেখা হয়, বন্ধুত্ব হয়। নীল পরিকে তারা ফুল তুলে দেয়, একসাথে খেলে। চলো দেখি, নীল পরির সাথে তারা আর কী কী করে?","language":"Bengali","langCode":"bn","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Uttam Kumar Dhar","Zahid Rahman"],"illustrators":["Mamun Hossain"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Room to Read","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/38514-nila-pari"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93913/size3/4ce4bc7307911968236428a8840e91a2.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/93913/size6/4ce4bc7307911968236428a8840e91a2.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74603/size6/5051f5bfe335c75d54174aee30897be6.jpg","text":"নদীর নাম পিয়াং।","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74604/size6/95f2f2637541c353c9aee2b2e7b7a9cc.jpg","text":"নদীর ওপার পাহাড়। \nনাম দিয়াং।","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74605/size6/fae9143f3ffaeb8a0f6ffef930a11295.jpg","text":"পাহাড়টার ওপর তিনা আর টিনার বাড়ি।","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74606/size6/c885452e3a91aacd5ed356c0e2cc1cfa.jpg","text":"ওরা দুজন পড়ার সাথী।","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74607/size6/e463eb1105d9662c7c532e981c2ab6fb.jpg","text":"তখন ভর দুপুর। \nচারপাশ ফাঁকা। \nতিনা আর টিনা হাঁটছিল।","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74608/size6/80c8f561f4c3378a4dc00d1ff244fb0e.jpg","text":"ওরা একটা বড় ঝিরি পাড়ি দিল।","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74610/size6/1ba5372b601bb92fb6410a524a0dbf9c.jpg","text":"হঠাৎ এক নীল পরি। \nবড় বড় পাখা।","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74611/size6/9cf60db94dad95db3de3e04dc568c061.jpg","text":"তিনা আর টিনা অবাক। আবার খুশিও।","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74612/size6/ca5345ca95d691c029ccfd72721d22cc.jpg","text":"নীল পরি ফুল চাইল। \nওরা জুঁই ফুল আনল।","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74613/size6/48d7dd76e479b031c343d88aa39f4dcd.jpg","text":"টগর ফুল আনল। \nজবা ফুল আনল।","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74615/size6/4fbacd8c90d3618231889a11ec2bb63e.jpg","text":"নীল পরি খুব খুশি।\nসব ফুল নিল নীল পরি।","words":null},{"n":12,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74616/size6/d229ac8a09fed513db62ee3785f3e795.jpg","text":"অাঁচল ভরল।\nতিনা আর টিনার হাত ধরল।","words":null},{"n":13,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74617/size6/1952762b78f10e7b1331480b618cf579.jpg","text":"নাচানাচি করল। \nএবার নীল পরির যাওয়ার পালা।","words":null},{"n":14,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74618/size6/9b0531ac0e4533126239f7d1ba60a2be.jpg","text":"তিনা আর টিনা বিদায় জানাল।","words":null},{"n":15,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/74619/size6/e6b509f94b666982c251f0f1d90160c7.jpg","text":"নীল পরিও বিদায় নিল। হাওয়ায় পাখা ভাসাল।\nবহু পথ পাড়ি দিল।","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":15,"words":99}}